  "texts": [
    "This approach could enhance the accuracy of emotional assessments and provide tailored support, but it warrants systematic evaluation of their effectiveness in producing reliable insights.It is important to note that although people want the chatbot to better understand their emotional status, it does not imply that in the future, emotional support chatbots can have full access to individuals' activities, from digital footprints to wearable device data.",
    "Directly using their digital activities or physical data to infer mental health-related status may raise privacy concerns, as certain parts of the data may contain sensitive information that individuals do not want to disclose [13,64].",
    "In addition, as chatbots receive more detailed information from individuals, the risk of privacy invasion increases due to the reasoning capabilities of LLMs [3,38].",
    "Thus, it is crucial to establish clear boundaries around data usage, ensure proper data anonymization and obtain consent from users.",
    "7.2.2 Leveraging AI to Integrate Multimodal Interactions."
  ],
